                                "MainContent": {
                                    "AnimationType": "FadeIn",
                                    "Excerpt": {
                                        "Title": "IK Mecha Spider",
                                        "Description": {
                                            "HorizontalTextAlignment": "Center",
                                            "Lines": [
                                                "The idea to create this project came from one of my favorite games from my childhood: <*Ratchet Deadlocked*>. In it, you could pilot an amazing Spider Robot that was really responsive. It’s flaw was that it was unable to walk on walls, only on regular ground. That’s what I wanted to accomplish with this project: a spider that was able to walk on almost <*any given surface*>."
                                            ]
                                        }
                                    }
                                },
                                "ContentPositioning": "MainContentOnly"
                            },
                            {
                                "MainContent": {
                                    "EmptyBlock": {
                                        "Size": 3
                                    }
                                }
                            },
                            {
                                "MainContent": {
                                    "AnimationType": "FadeInBottomTranslate",
                                    "Excerpt": {
                                        "Title": "Overview",
                                        "Description": {
                                            "HorizontalTextAlignment": "Left",
                                            "Lines": [
                                                "This robotic spider is capable of many things (including mass destruction of virtual worlds).",
                                                "One of its key features is the ability to walk on different kinds of surfaces, even on ceilings! Its greatest feature lies on its animation: it is not pre-baked, it uses <*procedurally generated animation*>, calculated at runtime. This enables each leg to <*adapt*>, individually, to the surface it is currently on!",
                                                "It also has some secondary features, like a simple but cool <*weapon system*> and a <*collision detection mechanism*>, that activates an energy shield when colliding with certain types of objects."
                                            ]
                                        },
                                        "Links": [
                                            {
                                                "IconRef": "fab fa-youtube",
                                                "Label": "Showcase",
                                                "Url": "https://youtu.be/9QNpkB4GmKI",
                                                "isEnabled": true
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "IconRef": "fab fa-unity",
                                                "Label": "Purchase (Deprecated)",
                                                "Url": "https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/3d/characters/robots/ik-mecha-spider-183484",
                                                "isEnabled": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    }
                                },
                                "ExtraContent": {
                                    "AnimationType": "FadeIn",
                                    "Image": {
                                        "Url": "images/ikmecha/render.png",
                                        "AltText": "IKMecha in a blank environment.",
                                        "OverlayGifUrl": ""
                                    }
                                },
